snippet.title: Venturous - A Superb Indiana Jones Inspired DOOM Total Conversion Mod Where You Hunt For Atlantis!
snippet.description:
Venturous - A Superb Indiana Jones Inspired DOOM Total Conversion Mod Where You Hunt For Atlantis!

Read More & Play The Mod: https://www.freegameplanet.com/venturous-doom-total-conversion-mod/

#Venturous #indianajones #doom 

00:00 Venturous Start
13:44 Mesoamerica Boss Battle
15:59 The Museum
21:25 Egypt
28:24 The Key
30:32 Captured
34:47 Going To Atlantis
54:20 Atlantis Boss Battle

This is a condensed playthrough that trims out some sections of the levels as they're pretty long. The full game takes around 2-3 hours to play through. I'm also using an additional Bolognese Gore mod for this video. The main mod is much less gory. The Gore mod is turned off for the final Atlantis level if you want to see what it's like without it.
